This recipe as printed here is incorrect. The amount of chicken broth listed in this recipe in The Gourmet Cookbook is 3/4 cup. And when you make it with only 1/4 cup, as I did tonight, you will see why! I have written to Epicurious but in the meantime, BEWARE! I will re-rate this after I make it with the correct amount of broth.

